>Unicron:
> 
>"Our time is near my child"said the massive planet 
>destroyer"soon the maximals and Predacons will suffer under our 
>might"

"Yes my lord" came Marauder's reply as he continued his descent into the open skies. "All will suffer, and you my lord Unicron will reign supreme!"

As he spoke his body began to shift, the sounds of gears grinding hallmarks of the transformation he was undergoing. After a moment there was no longer a star-fighter in the air but instead something far larger and far more dangerous: A dragon!

With great and powerful wings it cupped the air as it continued its descent!
